snippet.title: Astro Blox Revisted New Amiga Game by R3D
snippet.description:
Works on any Amiga with 512KB RAM. 100% pure assembler code.

Astro Blox Revisted Collector Box (included CD, DD Floppy Disk and poster) can be purchase here:
https://www.sordan.ie/product/765/astro-blox-revisted-amiga-game-box-cd-floppy-disk-poster-r3d/
